          "blocks": {
            "text_MAgJXd": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h2>Reduce what needs to be made.</h2><p>The goal is not simply to produce “better” clothing inside the same system. It is to produce less, more carefully, and with greater intention.</p><p>By using reclaimed textiles, Neuthread diverts fabric from disposal, extends the life of existing materials, and reduces the need for new production at the starting point.</p><p>Less waste. More imagination.</p><h2>Part of something wider.</h2><p>Neuthread is part of Daisy Chain, a charity supporting autistic and neurodivergent people and families across the North East.</p><p>Revenue from the brand helps support services, opportunities and long-term impact in the region. At the same time, the brand creates space for neurodiverse creativity to shape the design and making process itself.</p><p>This is not a separate story sitting beside the clothes. It is part of how the brand works.</p>",
                "width": "fit-content",
                "max_width": "none",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "rte",
